---
/**
 * HowItWorks.astro — "Solusi Irigasi Cerdas" & "Berdasarkan Penggunaan Nyata di Lapangan"
 * Design: Explains the smart irrigation solution approach
 */
---

<section
  id="solusi"
  class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-50 to-white"
  aria-labelledby="solusi-heading"
>
  <div class="container-wide mx-auto">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-primary-100 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-4">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z" />
          <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5" />
          <path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5" />
        </svg>
        Solusi Irigasi Cerdas
      </div>
      <h2 id="solusi-heading" class="section-title">
        Berdasarkan <span class="gradient-text">Penggunaan Nyata</span> di Lapangan
      </h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">
        Sistem irigasi ADOSISTERING dirancang berdasarkan penelitian dan pengalaman langsung di lahan pertanian Indonesia, menggunakan teknologi IoT yang telah terbukti.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Solution Steps -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="card text-center group">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 bg-primary-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary-200 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">Langkah 01</div>
        <h3 class="text-heading-sm text-neutral-900 mb-3">Sensor Mengumpulkan Data</h3>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-neutral-600">
          Sensor kelembaban tanah, suhu, dan cuaca mengumpulkan data real-time dari lahan pertanian secara otomatis dan akurat.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="card text-center group">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 bg-accent-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-accent-200 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-accent-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2" />
            <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21" />
            <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm font-bold text-accent-600 mb-2">Langkah 02</div>
        <h3 class="text-heading-sm text-neutral-900 mb-3">Platform Menganalisis</h3>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-neutral-600">
          Data dikirim ke platform cloud untuk dianalisis. Sistem menentukan kebutuhan irigasi optimal berdasarkan kondisi aktual.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="card text-center group">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 bg-primary-100 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary-200 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14" />
            <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm font-bold text-primary-600 mb-2">Langkah 03</div>
        <h3 class="text-heading-sm text-neutral-900 mb-3">Otomatis & Terkontrol</h3>
        <p class="text-body-sm text-neutral-600">
          Pompa air diaktifkan otomatis sesuai kebutuhan, atau dikontrol manual melalui website dan aplikasi dari mana saja.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
